        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/hybrid-tempest/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Press everything off cooldown while in &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the addition of Major Grandmaster trait &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;1675&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Inferno, burning you do now scales off of your Power instead of Condition Damage. This build attempts to maximise this trait by staying in &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement as much as possible.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build does ~45% of your total damage in Burning, with the remaining ~55% in Power, easily making it a Hybrid DPS build.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
