&lt;h2 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot; class=&quot;language-chatlink z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-chatlink&quot; data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-begin&quot;&gt;[&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;DQYfPSkfMBd0AHQAjgDLAMsAcwC+AVABJgAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAADVgAvAAkBAA==&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-end&quot;&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;5503,5535,5542,5734,5666&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;31,41,48&#x27; data-armory-31-traits=&#x27;296,334,1675&#x27; data-armory-41-traits=&#x27;232,1502,226&#x27; data-armory-48-traits=&#x27;1886,1891,1839&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation&quot;&gt;Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your rotation consists of a simple opener and a &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement priority.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opener:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start in &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5494&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Air Attunement&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cast &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29719&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Air as the start begins&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5561&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Lightning Strike (Scepter Air 2)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5529&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ride the Lightning (Dagger Air 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement Priority:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29706&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Fire&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5675&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phoenix (Scepter Fire 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5692&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Dragon&#x27;s Tooth (Scepter Fire 2)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5736&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Firestorm (&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5734&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Glyph of Storms in &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5542&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Fire&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5691&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ring of Fire (Dagger Fire 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5557&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Grab (Dagger Fire 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5666&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Glyph of Elementals&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Try to always start with your Opener before entering &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5494&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Air Attunement. As much as possible you want to hit your &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29719&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Air, but that is not always possible on all bosses. If you are lazy or do not want to do the opener, you can also just start in &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement, cast some skills, then proceed to &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29706&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Fire.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is important to press &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5675&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phoenix (Scepter Fire 3) and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5692&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Dragon&#x27;s Tooth (Scepter Fire 2) as much as possible as they are both blast finishers, and are critical to upkeep &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;104800&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of Bloodstone. In an actual fight, there will be many fields placed by your allies that you will be continuously blasting, but on the golem the only fields you have are from &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29706&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Fire and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5691&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ring of Fire. Therefore you might find yourself doing more damage in a fight than on the golem, especially since this build is not designed to maximise self blast finishers.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However, outside of &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29706&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Fire, &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5675&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phoenix (Scepter Fire 3), and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5692&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Dragon&#x27;s Tooth (Scepter Fire 2), it honestly doesn&#x27;t matter too much which order you push your buttons in, as long as you try your best to hit them off cooldown. I personally press most of my buttons from left to right on the keyboard for this build, as it is easier that way.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should also:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cast Off Cooldown:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30662&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Feel the Burn!&quot;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;25499&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Flame Barrage&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All of these skills have no cast time and can be cast anytime, even during &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29706&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Fire.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;crowd-control&quot;&gt;Crowd Control&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your CC skills are:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CC Skills:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5694&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Blinding Flash (Scepter Air 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5687&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Updraft (Dagger Air 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5696&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Dust Devil (Scepter Earth 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5690&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Earthquake (Dagger Earth 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5522&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Churning Earth (Dagger Earth 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately to CC, you will need to swap off &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement. This usually results in a DPS loss, but there is a small window, when your &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement is about ~7-10 seconds from coming off cooldown, where it would actually result in a DPS increase.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To CC, perform the following:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CC Rotation:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5495&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Earth Attunement&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5696&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Dust Devil (Scepter Earth 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5690&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Earthquake (Dagger Earth 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5522&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Churning Earth (Dagger Earth 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5494&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Air Attunement&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5694&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Blinding Flash (Scepter Air 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5687&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Updraft (Dagger Air 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5529&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ride the Lightning (Dagger Air 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5561&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Lightning Strike (Scepter Air 2)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29719&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Air&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then return to &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement as soon as you are able to.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This may seem to be an extremely long chain of skills, but it&#x27;s essentially just:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5495&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Earth Attunement 3 4 5&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5494&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Air Attunement 2 3 4 5&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29719&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Overload Air&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
